{"body": "```ruby\r\nrequire 'benchmark'\r\n\r\nkilobyte = \"1\" * 1024\r\n\r\nu = ActiveSupport::Multibyte::Unicode\r\n\r\nres = Benchmark.realtime do\r\n  10_000.times do\r\n    u.tidy_bytes(kilobyte)\r\n  end\r\nend\r\n\r\nputs \"tidy_bytes took #{res / 10}ms\"\r\n```\r\n\r\nSave as `./activesupport/bm.rb`, cd to `./activesupport`, and run:\r\n\r\n```\r\nruby -I./lib -ractive_support/multibyte/unicode bm.rb\r\n```\r\n\r\nOutput before proposed change:\r\n\r\n```\r\ntidy_bytes took 1.9525396000000002ms\r\n```\r\n\r\nAfter proposed change:\r\n\r\n```\r\ntidy_bytes took 0.0029686ms\r\n```", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/17052574", "created_at": "2013-04-26T02:36:28Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/10353#issuecomment-17052574", "updated_at": "2013-04-26T02:37:01Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 10353, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/burke/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/burke/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/burke/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/burke", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/burke/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/burke", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/burke/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/cdc3fc7e6309a7989b6f5467670ec3cd?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F242c100dc94f871b6d7215b868a875f8.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/burke/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/burke/received_events", "gravatar_id": "cdc3fc7e6309a7989b6f5467670ec3cd", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/burke/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "burke", "type": "User", "id": 1284, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/burke/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237df93bd3543c151008d04"}, "id": 17052574, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/10353"}
